headline: A Look At Principal Financial Group (PFG) Valuation After Strong Multi Year Shareholder Returns
summary: Principal Financial Group (PFG) has been drawing attention after a stretch of strong historical total returns, including 24.0% over the past year and 111.6% over the past 5 years, prompting fresh interest in its valuation. See our latest analysis for Principal Financial Group. The latest share price of US$95.5 comes after a 15.25% 90 day share price return, while the 24.01% 1 year total shareholder return points to momentum that has been building rather than fading.
